LocalizedProperties.ProductDescription:
Supports Xbox Play Anywhere: yours to play on both Xbox One and Windows 10 PC at no additional cost

Defunct is an indie adventure game with a focus on flow, speed and an engaging world. You are a broken robot that accidentally falls out of a giant cargo ship onto a post-human Earth, now inhabited by robots. You have to get back to your ship before it’s too late!
You are equipped with a Gravitize engine. It is used to create a separate gravity around yourself; this is the main source of your speed. Use this in downhills to accelerate. But be careful, using it uphill will slow you down. In addition to this the world is full of different speed boosts such as Enerjuice, which you can pick up and use to go faster.
LocalizedProperties.ShortDescription: Defunct is an indie adventure game with a focus on flow, speed and an engaging world. You are a broken robot that accidentally falls out of a giant cargo ship onto a post-human Earth, now inhabited by robots. You have to get back to your ship before it’s too late!

Features: High speed gameplay with unique ‘gravitation’ engine.
Traverse 11 varied levels full of different climates, biomes and challenges.
Unlock skins for the main character.
Compete for the best completion times in time trial mode (which features 5 extra levels).
LocalizedProperties.MinimumNotes: OS Version: Windows 7 or higher;Processor: 2.7 GHz Dual Core;Memory: 4 GB;Graphics: Nvidia Geforce GTX 670 or AMD Radeon HD 7977;DirectX Version: 18;Disk Space: 2 GB
LocalizedProperties.RecommendedNotes: OS Version: Windows 7 or higher;Processor: Intel® Core™ i5 4th Gen / AMD A10 series;Memory: 8 GB;Graphics: NVIDIA® GeForce® GTX 957;DirectX Version: 18;Disk Space: 3 GB
